{"tid":1097111,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android Q 將原生支援類似 3D Touch 的 Deep Press 螢幕感壓機能","createTime":"2019-04-08T07:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T14:03:05.000Z","uid":109383,"like":42,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"212e64bb0cc529928e17cdf913db0f4b90ab76a0","tid":1097111,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"在蘋果推出 3D Touch 技術之後， Android 陣營也有幾個品牌推出具備螢幕感壓的產品，但在缺乏生態圈的支援之下，多數具備螢幕趕鴨的 Android 設備只落得空有硬體缺乏應用的情形，不過 Google 似乎想為下一版 Android 、 Android Q 增添新特色，在最新釋出的 Android Q 開發版中，加入稱為 Deep Press 的原生螢幕感壓支援。<br />\n<br />\n不過除了支援 Deep Press 是螢幕感壓技術外，關於實際應用、是否需要特定硬體技術支援等都還不明確，但可預期的是一旦 Android Q 系統支援螢幕感壓，應該能多少帶動 app 開發者支援這項技術的意願。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndroid Q 手勢操作 或將近似 iPhone 風<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1067138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1067138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndroid Q 又抄iPhone 抄完手勢操作 又抄iOS11螢幕錄影 再抄3d touch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話Android好創新又突破？<br />\n<br />\n擺底預言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Android狗有得用3d touch之後 會話好好用 之後繼續屌Apple無突破 iOS抄Android乜乜乜功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61909103887f5af6eb1d65eb4910228a1156d401","tid":1097111,"uid":89514,"like":36,"dislike":6,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"297d4ba33f936d3a2715b11d48c202019aca2adb","tid":1097111,"uid":79355,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:34:06.000Z","msg":"iOS 唔係想cut走3D touch咩<br />\n而家先黎抄？"},{"pid":"c293276cf704002b13a9fec139344dc65222a402","tid":1097111,"uid":1552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T07:45:26.000Z","msg":"又抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},